channel.title: Help me get my 508 online? PLEASE READ!
channel.description: Alright, I'm just done making individual threads about what I need help with. Could someone just get on teamviewer and help me set it up? I've got everything ready, I just can't get it to allow other people to get on, and I have no idea how to do it. I'll give you specifics when you message me about helping me. I really need help with this, I have 10 people who are really counting on me to figure this out, but I really am at my wits end with these. PLEASE HELP!

item.title: Help me get my 508 online? PLEASE READ!
item.dc:creator: @Mr.czar Mr.czar
item.description:
@Mr.czar wrote:

[quote=“Davidi2, post:3, topic:408412”]Checklist:

  1. Is your server running? Make sure there was no error when you started the server
  2. Have you portfowarded properly? canyouseeme.org, try 43594[/quote]

Or what ever port you are using for your server like 5555 or ^ what he said.
